n = int(input())
    adj = [[] for _ in range(n)]
    for i in range(n-1):
        a, b = map(int, input().split())
        adj[a-1].append(b-1)
        adj[b-1].append(a-1)
    leaves = [i for i in range(n) if len(adj[i]) == 1]
    min_f = n
    max_f = 0
    for i in range(len(leaves)):
        for j in range(i+1, len(leaves)):
            f = 0
            q = [leaves[i]]
            visited = [False] * n
            visited[leaves[i]] = True
            while q:
                cur = q.pop()
                for v in adj[cur]:
                    if not visited[v]:
                        q.append(v)
                        visited[v] = True
                        f += 1
            if f < min_f:
                min_f = f
            if f > max_f:
                max_f = f
    print(min_f, max_f)
